This game is created by Mihai Baltac.

Controls:
w,a,s,d -> move the camera 

t,g -> zoom out and in

p -> pause and resume(when paused)

arrows -> move the falling box

When you put the falling box on the right trajectory(the vertical line that goes through it's center intersects the orizontal surface of the previous box), 
it turns red. Then, you can press <space> to make the box move faster to it's right position.

When you win or lose , a message would be displayed to let you know. Then you can press "r" to restart the game.

q -> to quit the game at any time